      <title>卡尼建议加拿大军队加强招募</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/carney-proposes-raises-for-canada-military-to-bolster-recruitment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）表示，他的政府将加速武装部队，加快对军事装备的收购，并授予加拿大海岸警卫队的新监视权，如果他赢得选举。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/carney-proposes-raises-for-canada-military-to-bolster-recruitment</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 12:47:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南苏丹反对派猛击乌干达的部署；联合国警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/south-sudan-opposition-slams-uganda-deployment-un-warns-of-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南苏丹四面楚歌的副总统说，乌干达军队在他的国家内部部署违反了联合国的武器禁运，并冒着崩溃的和平协议的风险，因为联合国警告该石油生产的国家处于内战的边缘。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/south-sudan-opposition-slams-uganda-deployment-un-warns-of-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 12:28:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院正在为特朗普政策进行法律摊牌的季节</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-supreme-court-cases-over-immigration-federal-spending-quickly-add-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部正在为唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统努力推动行政权力的努力而进行快速斗争，并在未来几周甚至几天内为美国最高法院提出了关键问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/trump-supreme-court-cases-over-immigration-federal-spending-quickly-add-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普设定截止日期时，核监管机构暗示伊朗会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/nuclear-watchdog-hints-at-iran-talks-soon-as-trump-sets-deadline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国核监管机构表示，其与一名伊朗高级官员的最新演讲未能在长达多年的原子探针中取得突破，这强调了迫切需要对外交解决方案，以实现伊斯兰共和国与美国之间的紧张对峙。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/nuclear-watchdog-hints-at-iran-talks-soon-as-trump-sets-deadline</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 11:00:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列批准预算，给内塔尼亚胡政治喘息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/israel-set-to-pass-budget-in-political-respite-for-netanyahu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列议会批准了今年的国家预算，在市场上发生动荡之后，政治上的本杰明·内塔尼亚胡（Benjamin Netanyahu）给了政治喘息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/israel-set-to-pass-budget-in-political-respite-for-netanyahu</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 10:39:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国部长说，里夫斯的免费音乐会门票不合适</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/uk-minister-says-reeves-free-concert-tickets-not-appropriate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国一位部长批评财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯（Rachel Reeves）接受音乐音乐会的免费门票，强调了她在统治工党中争取的斗争，只是她将在她发表春季财政声明的前一天，概述了预计总计数十亿英镑的削减。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/uk-minister-says-reeves-free-concert-tickets-not-appropriate</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 10:21:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
